Teslam ɣef wayen i d-nnan i tejmuyaɛ n watmaten n temdint n Lquds yellan di tmurt n Tyatir, ț-țamurt n Illirya di mkul amkan.
S wakka ur nețɣimi ara d arrac imeẓyanen i țțawint lemwaji, i gekkat waḍu ɣer mkul lǧiha, iwumi țkellixen yemdanen s tḥila-nsen d uselmed-nsen.
Akken daɣen i tedṛa d imezdaɣ n temdinin n Sur akk-d Sidun, neɣ m'ulac ad sekkren ccwal ger lɣaci, a t-iṭṭef di leḥzen, alamma d ass wis tlata a d-iḥyu si ger lmegtin.
Ulac-it dagi, mkul yiwen deg-sen ayen iwumi qqaṛen s yisem n Sidna Ɛisa Lmasiḥ ; meɛna mačči s ɣuṛ-es i d-yekka meɛna mi s-d-yenna : « Ur țțagadet ara, deg ussan-nni neɣ deg ussan i d-iteddun ».
D ayen yeɛnan kan lɛaddat n ccariɛa ɣef wučči ț-țissit akk-d luḍu ; lɛaddat-agi llant-ed d lemtel kan armi d asmi yerra Sidi Ṛebbi kullec d ajdid.
Llant dinna sețța n tsebbalin ( icmuxen ) yețwaxedmen s wedɣaɣ, țțawint si tmanyin ar meyya uɛecrin n litrat, seg-sent i d-țɛemmiṛen wat Isṛail aman i luḍu.
Di taddart-nni tella yiwet n tmeṭṭut yellan d yir tameṭṭut ; mi tesla s Sidna Ɛisa yella deg wexxam n wufarizi-nni, tekcem tewwi yid-es tabuqalt n leɛṭer.
